    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>carrot batons</strong>, <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>onion wedges</strong> and <strong>chicken thighs </strong>to a <strong>baking tray </strong>(or two!)</p><p>Pour over the<strong> spice rub</strong> and give everything a good mix up (clean hands are the best way!)</p><p>Make sure the<strong> chicken thighs </strong>are<strong> </strong>skin-side up on top of the other ingredients and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
