    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 50-60 min or until the chicken<strong> </strong>is golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) and the vegetables are tender - this is your <strong>Moroccan-style chicken, carrot & tomato tray bake</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
