    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken and<strong> </strong>vegetables have been in the oven for 45 min, boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>couscous</strong>, <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong> and <strong>sultanas</strong> to a heatproof bowl with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiling water</strong>, cover and set aside</p>",
