      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped dill</strong> with your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> in a small bowl and give it a good mix up – this is your<strong> dill yoghurt</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
